{"tid":1346363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年跪地求饒望停手    助白衣人尋眼鏡後被重拳擊倒","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:16:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":159,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"20d7bdc46ae1068935b54c69ba42c891544eaecc","tid":1346363,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190722/_2019072209003269683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190722%2F_2019072209003269683.jpg&h=32c86c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大批白衣人昨晚在元朗聚集，無定向毆打市民，更衝入港鐵站用棍和雨傘狂毆乘客，傷者人數增至45人，其中1名男子危殆，另有5人情況嚴重。其中在車廂中，一名被打年青男子跪地求饒，最後被一名白衣人重拳擊倒。<br />\n<br />\n該名年青男子要求白衣人停手，跪地向眾白衣人表示「唔好咁啦」，期間一直有女乘客在旁哭泣，其後白衣人要求「攞返副眼鏡嚟先」，他隨後在地上拾起眼鏡遞予對方，期間一名持棍穿藍衣的男子向他頭部揮重拳，青年隨即倒地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1049615/即時-香港-元朗暴力-青年跪地求饒望停手-助白衣人尋眼鏡後被重拳擊倒\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1049615%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%AA%E5%9C%B0%E6%B1%82%E9%A5%92%E6%9C%9B%E5%81%9C%E6%89%8B-%E5%8A%A9%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8B%E7%9C%BC%E9%8F%A1%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E9%87%8D%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A%E5%80%92&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=4e615dc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1049615%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%AA%E5%9C%B0%E6%B1%82%E9%A5%92%E6%9C%9B%E5%81%9C%E6%89%8B-%E5%8A%A9%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8B%E7%9C%BC%E9%8F%A1%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E9%87%8D%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A%E5%80%92&h=184df669\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1049615/即時-香港-元朗暴力-青年跪地求饒望停手-助白衣人尋眼鏡後被重拳擊倒</a>"},{"pid":"57cf2bfd55698f